title: War of the Roses: Solo Cabin Trips
description: Andy never really mistrusted his wife Sara but a friend got into his head and now he's questioning her solo trips to their cabin.  Andy's friend told him his wife was doing "solo" trips to the cabin and then found out she was cheating on him so now that got in Andy's head and he's questioning Sara's cabin trips.
